PrecisOrder (a) designating the OFFICE OF MARINE SAFETY, Department of Transport, as the SHIPPING OFFICE for 31 ports throughout Canada, and (b) designating those ports as ports at which the shipping master, deputy shipping master and such clerks and servants as are necessary for the proper conduct of the shipping office, may be appointed.
